</div>',
'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1554224155-8d04cb21cd6e?w=800&q=80',
'technology', 'EagleView alternatives, roof measurement cost, aerial measurements, Atlanta, Phoenix, Denver, contractor tools, ROI',
'RoofReporterAI Team', 'published', 1,
